name: fsl-pyfeeds
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "fsl-pyfeeds" %}
{% set version = "0.8.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "7c10d6b3ab242ca20b28bab2b0298260c5f5bf42893f4052491fc2e9ab6b8f73" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"
  entry_points:
    - pyfeeds = pyfeeds.main:main

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - numpy >=1.11
    - nibabel >=2.1

test:
  imports:
    - pyfeeds
  commands:
    - pyfeeds -V

about:
  home: https://git.fmrib.ox.ac.uk/fsl/pyfeeds
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'FSL testing framework'
  dev_url: https://git.fmrib.ox.ac.uk/fsl/pyfeeds

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pauldmccarthy
